<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
</head>
<body>
  <div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;">
    <div style="background-color: #4f46e5; padding: 20px; text-align: center;">
      <h1 style="color: white; margin: 0;">Parental Consent Required</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div style="padding: 20px;">
      <p>Hello,</p>
      
      <p>Your child, <strong><%= @user.full_name %></strong> (age <%= @user.age %>), has requested access to features on our platform that require parental consent.</p>
      
      <p>To grant permission for your child to access age-appropriate content, please click the button below:</p>
      
      <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
        <%= link_to "Grant Consent", parental_consent_url(token: @user.consent_token), 
            style: "display: inline-block; background-color: #4f46e5; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; font-weight: bold;" %>
      </div>
      
      <p>This consent will allow your child to participate in age-restricted spaces and activities on our platform.</p>
      
      <p>If you did not request this or believe it's in error, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
      
      <p>Thank you,<br>
      The Access Control Team</p>
    </div>
    
    <div style="background-color: #f3f4f6; padding: 15px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #6b7280;">
      <p>© <%= Time.current.year %> Access Control System. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
